Start by saving the script as a python file (.py)
Upload it to Elektronik AG windows file by a direct network transfer (ask IT team for the IP address and credentials and enter them in remote desktop connection)
Install the (requests, pandas) libraries & ensure python 3 is installed 
use our provided api key to gain and enter it in the script
use windows task scheduler to rerun the script at the desired intervals
in task scheduler choose create basic task, trigger timing, and our python script to have it run the code at our desired intervals
use our created text file sync_log.txt to check our code status (code run successfully or potential error codes)
